---
/**
 * Skills.astro
 * Terminal-styled skills display with system status indicators
 */
---

<section class="terminal-skills">
  <div class="terminal-window">
    <div class="terminal-header">
      <div class="terminal-buttons">
        <span class="btn-close"></span>
        <span class="btn-minimize"></span>
        <span class="btn-maximize"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-title">wolf@hrt:~/skills</div>
      <div class="terminal-status">
        <span class="status-indicator online"></span>
        <span>ONLINE</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-content">
      <div class="terminal-prompt">
        <span class="prompt-user">wolf</span>
        <span class="prompt-at">@</span>
        <span class="prompt-host">hrt</span>
        <span class="prompt-colon">:</span>
        <span class="prompt-path">~</span>
        <span class="prompt-dollar">$</span>
        <span class="prompt-command">neofetch --skills</span>
      </div>

      <div class="skills-output">
        <pre class="ascii-art">{`
 ██╗    ██╗ ██████╗ ██╗     ███████╗
 ██║    ██║██╔═══██╗██║     ██╔════╝
 ██║ █╗ ██║██║   ██║██║     █████╗
 ██║███╗██║██║   ██║██║     ██╔══╝
 ╚███╔███╔╝╚██████╔╝███████╗██║
  ╚══╝╚══╝  ╚═════╝ ╚══════╝╚═╝
`}</pre>

        <div class="system-info">
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">OS</span>
            <span class="info-value">Arch Linux x86_64</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Role</span>
            <span class="info-value">Trading Operations Analyst</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Location</span>
            <span class="info-value">London, UK</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Uptime</span>
            <span class="info-value uptime">Loading...</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Stack</span>
            <span class="info-value">Rust, Python, Go, K8s</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Focus</span>
            <span class="info-value">SRE / DevOps / Trading Systems</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-blocks">
        <div class="skill-block">
          <div class="block-header">
            <span class="block-icon">[SYS]</span>
            <span class="block-title">Infrastructure & Operations</span>
          </div>
          <div class="block-content">
            <p>Ensuring trading systems run at peak performance. Monitoring, debugging, and optimizing high-frequency infrastructure across global markets.</p>
            <div class="tech-tags">
              <span class="tag">Kubernetes</span>
              <span class="tag">Prometheus</span>
              <span class="tag">Grafana</span>
              <span class="tag">Kafka</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="block-status">
            <span class="status-dot green"></span>
            <span>All systems operational</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill-block">
          <div class="block-header">
            <span class="block-icon">[DEV]</span>
            <span class="block-title">Systems Programming</span>
          </div>
          <div class="block-content">
            <p>Building low-latency trading tools and automation. From rapid debugging scripts to production-grade system utilities in Rust and Python.</p>
            <div class="tech-tags">
              <span class="tag">Rust</span>
              <span class="tag">Python</span>
              <span class="tag">C++</span>
              <span class="tag">Bash</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="block-status">
            <span class="status-dot green"></span>
            <span>0 errors, 0 warnings</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="skill-block">
          <div class="block-header">
            <span class="block-icon">[NET]</span>
            <span class="block-title">Market Connectivity</span>
          </div>
          <div class="block-content">
            <p>Direct experience with major exchanges: XLON, XETRA, TP/ICAP. Understanding market microstructure and trading protocols.</p>
            <div class="tech-tags">
              <span class="tag">FIX Protocol</span>
              <span class="tag">Exchange APIs</span>
              <span class="tag">Market Data</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="block-status">
            <span class="status-dot green"></span>
            <span>Markets connected</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="terminal-prompt bottom-prompt">
        <span class="prompt-user">wolf</span>
        <span class="prompt-at">@</span>
        <span class="prompt-host">hrt</span>
        <span class="prompt-colon">:</span>
        <span class="prompt-path">~</span>
        <span class="prompt-dollar">$</span>
        <span class="cursor">█</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  function updateUptime() {
    const startDate = new Date('2025-06-01');
    const now = new Date();
    const diff = now.getTime() - startDate.getTime();

    const days = Math.floor(diff / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));
    const hours = Math.floor((diff % (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)) / (1000 * 60 * 60));
    const mins = Math.floor((diff % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60));

    const uptimeEl = document.querySelector('.uptime');
    if (uptimeEl) {
      uptimeEl.textContent = `${days}d ${hours}h ${mins}m @ HRT`;
    }
  }

  updateUptime();
  setInterval(updateUptime, 60000);
</script>

<style>
  .terminal-skills {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .terminal-window {
    background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.95);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-secondary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 20px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15),
      0 0 40px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.05),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .terminal-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(30, 30, 40, 0.9) 0%, rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.9) 100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
  }

  .terminal-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .terminal-buttons span {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .btn-close { background: #ff5f57; }
  .btn-minimize { background: #ffbd2e; }
  .btn-maximize { background: #28ca42; }

  .terminal-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--gray-300);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .terminal-status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #28ca42;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .status-indicator {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse-glow 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .status-indicator.online {
    background: #28ca42;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px #28ca42;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-glow {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; }
  }

  .terminal-content {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .terminal-prompt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .prompt-user { color: #28ca42; }
  .prompt-at { color: var(--gray-400); }
  .prompt-host { color: var(--accent-secondary); }
  .prompt-colon { color: var(--gray-400); }
  .prompt-path { color: #a855f7; }
  .prompt-dollar { color: var(--gray-300); margin-right: 0.5rem; }
  .prompt-command { color: var(--gray-100); }

  .cursor {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  .skills-output {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .skills-output {
      flex-direction: row;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  .ascii-art {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    margin: 0;
    white-space: pre;
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .ascii-art {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
    }
  }

  .system-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .info-row {
    display: flex;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .info-label {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    min-width: 100px;
  }

  .info-label::after {
    content: ':';
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  .info-value {
    color: var(--gray-200);
  }

  .skill-blocks {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .skill-blocks {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  .skill-block {
    background: rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .skill-block:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-secondary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .block-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .block-icon {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .block-title {
    color: var(--gray-100);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .block-content p {
    color: var(--gray-400);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  .block-status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }

  .status-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .status-dot.green {
    background: #28ca42;
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px #28ca42;
  }

  .bottom-prompt {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .status-indicator,
    .cursor {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
